/**
 * /api/recommend
 *
 * Session-aware hybrid retrieval + narrowing chat + RAG-grounded recommendation.
 *
 * Flow:
 *   1. Receive intakeForm + messages + sessionState
 *   2. If no sessionState → create session, run hybrid retrieval → initial candidatePool
 *   3. Run question engine on candidatePool
 *   4. If question → LLM polishes & returns question + chips + candidateSnapshot
 *   5. If resolved → build evidence-grounded recommendation
 *
 * Hallucination prevention:
 *   - Product codes, specs, stock, lead time NEVER generated by LLM
 *   - Cutting conditions ONLY from evidence-chunks.json
 *   - LLM only writes natural-language explanation of real results
 */

